title: (Fri Full) Scotty McCreery on Finding Out He’s Going to Be A Dad and Reacts to Bobby Not Saying the Title of His New song + President’s Quiz
itunes:title: (Fri Full) Scotty McCreery on Finding Out He’s Going to Be A Dad and Reacts to Bobby Not Saying the Title of His New song + President’s Quiz
description:
Scotty McCreery is on to talk about his song “Damn Strait” and why Bobby won’t say the title of the song. He also shares the story of finding out he was going to become a dad and where he and his wife are picking out names. In honor of 4th of July weekend, Bobby tests the show’s presidential knowledge. They each have 5 minutes to write as many presidents as they can remember. The winner gets a prize!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
